vice-1,RuleTriggerMethodAdapter.injectTriggerPoint : inserting trigger into hipstershop.AdService.getRandomAds() java.util.List for rule AdService-getRandomAds-exception-1749323409,出现次数:1\naiops-k8s-08,adservice,adservice-2,org.jboss.byteman.agent.Transformer : inserted trigger for AdService-getRandomAds-exception-1749323409 in class hipstershop.AdService,出现次数:1\naiops-k8s-08,adservice,adservice-2,RuleTriggerMethodAdapter.injectTriggerPoint : inserting trigger into hipstershop.AdService.getRandomAds() java.util.List for rule AdService-getRandomAds-exception-1749323409,出现次数:1\naiops-k8s-08,adservice,adservice-2,org.jboss.byteman.agent.Transformer : possible trigger for rule AdService-getRandomAds-exception-1749323409 in class hipstershop.AdService,出现次数:1\naiops-k8s-07,adservice,adservice-1,org.jboss.byteman.agent.Transformer : possible trigger for rule AdService-getRandomAds-exception-1749323409 in class hipstershop.AdService,出现次数:1\naiops-k8s-03,frontend,frontend-0,\"{\"\"error\"\":\"\"failed to get ads: rpc error: code = Unknown desc = \"\",\"\"http.req.id\"\":\"\"3decad0f-26d7-47a3-b521-c8567290114d\"\",\"\"http.req.method\"\":\"\"GET\"\",\"\"http.req.path\"\":\"\"/product/1YMWWN1N4O\"\",\"\"message\"\":\"\"failed to retrieve ads\"\",\"\"session\"\":\"\"d2091e9d-915a-4af2-9fa9-7fb49a8b980b\"\",\"\"severity\"\":\"\"warning\"\",\"\"timestamp\"\":\"\"2025-06-07T19:23:20.05940681Z\"\"}\",出现次数:1\n", "unique_entities": {"pod_name": ["frontend-0", "frontend-2", "frontend-1", "adservice-0", "adservice-2", "adservice-1"], "service_name": ["frontend", "adservice"], "node_name": ["aiops-k8s-03", "aiops-k8s-04", "aiops-k8s-07", "aiops-k8s-08"]}, "matched_anomaly": "A fault was detected from 2025-06-07T19:10:08Z to 2025-06-07T19:24:08Z. Please analyze its root cause.", "time_range": "2025-06-07 19:10:08+00:00 to 2025-06-07 19:24:08+00:00"}, "log_data_collected": true, "log_analysis_findings": "根据日志分析结果，以下是验证根因假设的结论：\n\n### 分析结果\n1. **错误模式**:\n   - `frontend` 服务频繁报告 `failed to get ads: rpc error: code = Unknown desc =`，表明其无法从 `adservice` 获取广告数据。\n   - `adservice` 服务出现大量与 Byteman 代理相关的错误，如 `Agent failed to start!`、`java.lang.Error: Injected error` 和 `Rule.execute called for AdService-getRandomAds-exception-1749323409`。\n\n2. **关键日志关键词**:\n   - `java.lang.Error: Injected error`\n   - `Agent failed to start`\n   - `Byteman agent injection errors`\n   - `failed to get ads`\n\n3. **公共嫌疑人**:\n   - 多个 `frontend` 实例抱怨 `adservice` 无法提供广告数据，而 `adservice` 的日志中明确显示了 Byteman 代理注入错误。\n\n### 结论\n根因假设 **'adservice is the root cause due to Byteman agent injection errors causing service failure'** 成立。日志中明确显示了 `adservice` 的 Byteman 代理注入错误，导致其无法正常提供服务，进而引发 `frontend` 的级联故障。\n\n### 输出 JSON\n```json\n{\n  \"stance\": \"SUPPORT\",\n  \"detected_log_keys\": [\n    \"java.lang.Error: Injected error\",\n    \"Agent failed to start\",\n    \"Byteman agent injection errors\",\n    \"failed to get ads\"\n  ],\n  \"hypotheses\": [\n    {\n      \"component\": \"adservice\",\n      \"reason\": \"Byteman agent injection errors causing service failure\",\n      \"evidence\": \"Exception in thread \\\"grpc-default-executor-1084\\\" java.lang.Error: Injected error\"\n    }\n  ]\n}\n```", "metric_analysis_findings": "基于获取到的指标数据分析，我来验证\"adservice is the root cause due to Byteman agent injection errors causing service failure\"这一假设。\n\n从指标数据来看：\n\n**不支持该假设的证据：**\n1. **adservice指标变化轻微**：adservice-0的error_ratio和client_error_ratio变化率仅为0.4736，属于中等程度变化，远不是最严重的异常\n2. **其他服务表现更差**：cartservice-1的rrt_max变化率为1.422，currencyservice-1的rrt_max变化率为1.3057，这些服务的延迟问题比adservice更严重\n3. **没有明显的资源瓶颈**：pod_cpu_usage等资源指标变化较小，没有发现adservice相关的资源异常\n\n**关键发现：**\n- 最严重的性能问题出现在cartservice-1和currencyservice-1\n- redis-cart-0的CPU使用率有轻微上升（变化率1.2299）\n- 节点资源使用率相对稳定，没有明显的资源瓶颈\n\n```json\n{\n  \"stance\": \"OPPOSE\",\n  \"detected_metric_keys\": [\"rrt_max\", \"rrt\", \"error_ratio\", \"client_error_ratio\", \"pod_cpu_usage\", \"node_cpu_usage_rate\", \"node_memory_usage_rate\"],\n  \"hypotheses\": [\n    {\n      \"component\": \"cartservice-1\",\n      \"reason\": \"rrt_max指标显示最大响应时间显著增加，变化率达1.422，是系统中最严重的性能问题\",\n      \"evidence\": \"cartservice-1的rrt_max从正常中位数7912.0上升到故障中位数7057.0，P99值从61428.76上升到10375.85\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"component\": \"currencyservice-1\", \n      \"reason\": \"rrt_max指标显示最大响应时间大幅恶化，变化率为1.3057\",\n      \"evidence\": \"currencyservice-1的rrt_max从4776.0上升到5083.5，P99值从13628.44飙升到64891.67\"\n    }\n  ]\n}\n```\n\n**结论**：指标数据不支持adservice是根本原因的假设。数据显示cartservice和currencyservice的性能问题更为严重，而adservice的异常相对轻微。", "trace_analysis_findings": "基于trace数据分析，我来验证\"adservice是根因由于Byteman代理注入错误导致服务故障\"这一假设。\n\n分析trace数据发现：\n\n1. **adservice调用确实存在延迟问题**：\n   - `frontend-2->frontend-2`调用adservice的GetAds操作：正常平均耗时5556ms，异常时14627ms（延迟倍数2.6倍）\n   - `frontend-1->frontend-1`调用adservice的GetAds操作：正常平均耗时5549ms，异常时11824ms（延迟倍数2.1倍）\n\n2. **但状态码显示adservice仍在正常运行**：\n   - 所有adservice调用都返回状态码2（正常），没有错误状态码\n   - 这意味着adservice虽然响应变慢，但服务本身没有完全失败\n\n3. **更严重的延迟问题出现在其他服务**：\n   - cartservice的AddItem操作：延迟倍数高达8.6倍（正常3785ms，异常32501ms）\n   - redis存储操作：延迟倍数7.5倍（正常1655ms，异常17982ms）\n   - paymentservice的Charge操作：延迟倍数5.7倍\n\n4. **错误传播路径分析**：\n   - 从拓扑结构看，adservice是相对独立的服务，主要被frontend调用\n   - 没有发现adservice错误向上游传播的证据\n\n```json\n{\n  \"stance\": \"OPPOSE\",\n  \"detected_trace_keys\": [\"rrt_max\", \"frontend->adservice\", \"cartservice->redis\", \"frontend->cartservice\", \"checkoutservice->paymentservice\"],\n  \"hypotheses\": [\n    {\n      \"component\": \"cartservice/redis\",\n      \"reason\": \"rrt_max\",\n      \"evidence\": \"cartservice AddItem操作延迟倍数8.6倍，redis存储操作延迟倍数7.5倍，远高于adservice的2.1-2.6倍延迟\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"component\": \"adservice\",\n      \"reason\": \"rrt_max\", \n      \"evidence\": \"adservice GetAds操作延迟倍数2.1-2.6倍，但状态码全部正常(2)，没有错误注入导致的失败证据\"\n    }\n  ]\n}\n```\n\n**结论**：我反对该假设。虽然adservice确实存在延迟增加，但：\n- trace数据中没有发现Byteman错误注入导致的失败证据\n- adservice所有调用都返回正常状态码(2)\n- 其他服务（特别是cartservice/redis）的延迟问题更加严重\n- adservice的延迟问题可能是系统级联故障的受害者而非根因"}
